==文化影響==
史矛革對於後世文學作品中龍的形象有著重要影響<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://io9.gizmodo.com/why-smaug-still-matters-1478936553|title=Why Smaug Still Matters|last=Davis|first=Lauren|date=2013-08-12|newspaper=io9|accessdate=2018-10-14|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181014091442/https://io9.gizmodo.com/why-smaug-still-matters-1478936553|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2012年《[[富比士|富比士]]》雜誌的虛構角色富豪榜上，史矛革名列第一<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.sohu.com/20120509/n342747529.shtml|title=福布斯2012虚拟人物财富榜：巨龙史矛革跃居首富|accessdate=2018-07-15|date=2012-05-09|publisher=搜狐新闻|archive-date=2018-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715210948/http://news.sohu.com/20120509/n342747529.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/ent/film/sinacn/20131008/05195043685.html|title=《霍比特人2》發中文預告 噴火巨龍亮嗓|accessdate=2018-07-15|date=2013-10-08|publisher=新浪網|archive-date=2018-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715210713/http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/ent/film/sinacn/20131008/05195043685.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但在2013年的虛構角色富豪榜則下降至第二名<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/special-report/2013/fictional-15/smaug.html|title=Smaug on the Forbes Fictional 15|newspaper=Forbes|accessdate=2018-07-15|language=en|archive-date=2018-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715211240/https://www.forbes.com/special-report/2013/fictional-15/smaug.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年，一種新被發現的[[角蝽科|角蝽科]]昆蟲被命名為「史矛革」<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://entomologytoday.org/2015/06/19/patagonian-shield-bug-named-after-middles-earths-smaug-the-dragon/|title=Patagonian Shield Bug Named After Middle's Earth's Smaug the Dragon|date=2015-06-19|newspaper=Entomology Today|accessdate=2018-07-15|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701165333/https://entomologytoday.org/2015/06/19/patagonian-shield-bug-named-after-middles-earths-smaug-the-dragon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

